O R D E R


On September 29, 2003, Respondent was suspended 
  from the practice of law for a period of thirty days.Â  He has now filed an affidavit 
  requesting reinstatement pursuant to Rule 32, of the Rules for Lawyer Disciplinary 
  Enforcement contained in Rule 413, SCACR.
The request is granted and he is hereby 
  reinstated to the practice of law in this state.&nbsp;

  
